column5: Are ya'll getting any rain yet? With the current low lake level is the passage from Ash Rapids to Shoal Lake navigable?

http://www.lwcb.ca/noticeboard.html Please read the red warning on this notice. It sounds like the LOW/Rainy River/Ifalls/Rainy Lake area is getting rain this weekend. Hopefully it will all fill up soon. We are headed up this weekend-that has been known to bring rain.
Rain predicted for this coming weekend, up to 2 inchs. I haven't been out to the area you asked about but I have to think it will be tricky get thru there.
